# Welcome to TDLive Minecraft!

TDLive Minecraft is a community project and we're always looking for people to join our community and help out. We love our users, and we hope our users love us!

# Projects
## Alice
Alice is the engine that holds everything in Paperbook together. Whether it's missions, teleporting, or just getting that NPC to say something, Alice is the engine for that.

**NOTE: If you look at the code, spoliers may be revealed!!!**

[Project on GitHub](http://github.com/TDLive-Minecraft/Alice)
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
